    "description": {
      "content": "The Mistral AI Chat Completions API enables developers to interact with Mistral's language models in a conversational manner. It supports multi-turn conversations, function calling, JSON mode for structured outputs, and vision capabilities. The API provides access to a range of models including Mistral Large, Mistral Small, and Codestral, each optimized for different use cases from general reasoning to code generation.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Mistral AI Support",
